description: It was very cold outside today so I decided to look around a train station. It turned out to be a superb choice of hunting ground. I met two boys from eastern parts of the Czech Republic. Honza and Tomas were in Prague for a weekend party. I noticed them when they were resting in the hallway, waiting for the next train home. They were quite tired but having too much time on their hands, they were willing to have a little chat with me. They spent almost all the money they had over the weekend. I had more than 50 000 waiting in my pocket. And it was a good idea to take this much today. The boys didn´t take too much convincing to join me in a nasty and crazy threesome. We had so much fun they almost missed their train home.
title: Czech Hunter 288
